kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:00:37.420 --> 00:00:41.300
=Eternal Joy With You=
=Episode 11=

00:00:42.900 --> 00:00:47.260
(Capital City)

00:00:56.280 --> 00:00:58.110
Come on. Keep up.

00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:08.870
Thank you for escorting us.

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:10.280
We are deeply grateful.

00:01:10.710 --> 00:01:12.590
Our paths diverge after entering the city.

00:01:12.870 --> 00:01:13.950
Guess this is where we part.

00:01:15.910 --> 00:01:17.000
I have little to do today.

00:01:17.350 --> 00:01:18.440
I'll see you a bit further.

00:01:18.700 --> 00:01:19.750
It'll put my mind at ease.

00:01:20.660 --> 00:01:21.540
Mother,

00:01:21.560 --> 00:01:23.510
let's go with Master a bit further.

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:25.560
Ruyi and I haven't finished talking yet.

00:01:26.590 --> 00:01:29.040
Yes, Aunt Ning. Just a little further.

00:01:33.590 --> 00:01:36.120
Sorry for the bother, Commander.

00:01:36.280 --> 00:01:37.120
No bother at all.

00:01:38.920 --> 00:01:40.120
This place is enormous.

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:43.000
Everything looks so new and exciting.

00:01:43.150 --> 00:01:44.760
And lots of delicious food.

00:01:45.590 --> 00:01:47.680
The air's filled with appetizing smells.

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:49.710
All right, you two little foodies.

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:52.310
I'll take you to Zuixiang Pavilion
for a big meal

00:01:52.310 --> 00:01:53.920
to satisfy your cravings, okay?

00:01:54.230 --> 00:01:55.070
Okay.

00:01:59.870 --> 00:02:01.760
What plans do you have after returning home?

00:02:01.950 --> 00:02:04.950
I plan to settle down
with Chang'an and Ruyi.

00:02:05.430 --> 00:02:06.560
No longer considering

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:08.520
finding someone to grow old with?

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:15.310
I've suffered enough in marriage.

00:02:15.310 --> 00:02:17.000
I don't want to step into that trap again.

00:02:18.430 --> 00:02:19.590
I'm better off by myself.

00:02:23.150 --> 00:02:24.280
Enough about me.

00:02:24.460 --> 00:02:25.710
Commander Pei, what about you?

00:02:26.030 --> 00:02:27.630
Is there someone you fancy?

00:02:27.870 --> 00:02:28.960
Same here.

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:31.120
Being single suits me.

00:02:35.590 --> 00:02:36.430
All right then.

00:02:37.240 --> 00:02:38.560
Now we're back,

00:02:38.910 --> 00:02:40.590
guess this might be goodbye for a while.

00:02:41.910 --> 00:02:43.560
Take care of yourself.

00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:46.190
I am the master of Chang'an and Ruyi.

00:02:46.790 --> 00:02:48.380
If we want to meet, we'll find a way.

00:02:52.750 --> 00:02:53.590
Get in the carriage.

00:03:12.240 --> 00:03:14.080
Princess, if Commander Pei knew

00:03:14.470 --> 00:03:16.430
you had waited for so long

00:03:16.590 --> 00:03:17.960
just to see him,

00:03:17.960 --> 00:03:20.080
he'd be touched by your sincerity.

00:03:20.080 --> 00:03:21.080
You and your smooth talk.

00:03:22.030 --> 00:03:22.870
However,

00:03:23.190 --> 00:03:25.310
I can't stop smiling thinking

00:03:25.630 --> 00:03:27.560
about seeing Heng.

00:03:29.630 --> 00:03:30.520
Princess, look.

00:03:30.800 --> 00:03:31.910
Isn't that Commander Pei?

00:03:43.800 --> 00:03:45.000
Greetings, Princess Anle.

00:03:45.590 --> 00:03:47.630
Heng, it's been so long.

00:03:49.960 --> 00:03:50.800
Princess Anle.

00:03:51.560 --> 00:03:52.400
Wanning,

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:57.590
why are you traveling with Heng?

00:03:59.910 --> 00:04:02.560
Commander Pei helped me with the divorce.

00:04:02.910 --> 00:04:04.960
He took pity on our plight

00:04:04.960 --> 00:04:06.820
and decided to see us home.

00:04:08.800 --> 00:04:11.280
When you met Cui Yunfeng

00:04:11.630 --> 00:04:13.150
back at the poetry gathering,

00:04:13.560 --> 00:04:16.430
I had no idea he'd be that morally rotten.

00:04:17.310 --> 00:04:18.430
Now that I think of it,

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:20.100
if it weren't for my involvement,

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:21.030
you'd never have...

00:04:21.040 --> 00:04:23.050
Princess, you do me too much honor
with such words.

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:26.270
It was my fault
that your name was stained back then.

00:04:26.600 --> 00:04:28.240
All this time I've carried this remorse

00:04:28.430 --> 00:04:29.830
without offering a proper apology.

00:04:29.970 --> 00:04:31.680
You were kind enough to introduce me to him,

00:04:31.830 --> 00:04:32.920
but who could have guessed

00:04:32.920 --> 00:04:35.160
the darkness hidden within his family?

00:04:36.390 --> 00:04:37.600
I strayed into a dead end.

00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:39.630
Fortunately, I have now turned back in time.

00:04:40.270 --> 00:04:41.430
I'm blessed as it is.

00:04:42.040 --> 00:04:43.750
Please don't concern yourself with me.

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:52.800
You must haven't met in a long time.

00:04:53.180 --> 00:04:54.750
There must still be a lot to talk about.

00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:56.440
Princess,

00:04:56.510 --> 00:04:57.800
I'll come by another day.

00:04:57.830 --> 00:04:59.180
I won't keep you any longer today.

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:01.200
Mm.

00:05:01.510 --> 00:05:02.600
I promised to see you home.

00:05:04.920 --> 00:05:06.140
How could I leave you halfway?

00:05:09.750 --> 00:05:11.950
Princess, please excuse me.

00:05:21.460 --> 00:05:23.160
(Xu Residence)
I'm grateful, Commander Pei.

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:24.190
We're home now.

00:05:24.680 --> 00:05:25.520
Come.

00:05:26.190 --> 00:05:27.280
Say goodbye to your master.

00:05:29.830 --> 00:05:32.190
Aunt Ning, I want to go with Master.

00:05:32.320 --> 00:05:34.060
You have Chang'an with you,

00:05:34.270 --> 00:05:36.160
but Master has no one.

00:05:36.390 --> 00:05:37.830
I don't want him to be alone.

00:05:37.920 --> 00:05:40.360
Besides, I want
to learn martial arts from Master.

00:05:44.160 --> 00:05:47.040
Mother, Ruyi and I discussed this.

00:05:47.120 --> 00:05:49.600
If I miss her, I'll go see her.

00:05:49.630 --> 00:05:51.390
If she misses me, she'll come to me.

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:53.000
That way, we'll be able to meet,

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:54.680
and you'll be able to meet Master as well.

00:06:03.750 --> 00:06:04.630
If that's the case,

00:06:05.040 --> 00:06:06.560
I'll take Ruyi back.

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:09.040
Lady Xu, please return home and rest.

00:06:10.430 --> 00:06:11.800
Is this appropriate?

00:06:24.200 --> 00:06:25.040
Let's go.

00:06:25.070 --> 00:06:26.160
Be careful on the road.

00:06:27.180 --> 00:06:31.780
(Xu Residence)

00:06:33.950 --> 00:06:35.270
When did you plan this?

00:06:36.360 --> 00:06:37.200
What?

00:06:37.860 --> 00:06:40.300
(Commander's Mansion)

00:06:41.560 --> 00:06:42.870
How lovely!

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:50.950
Master, is all this for me?

00:06:54.390 --> 00:06:55.270
Do you like it?

00:06:55.750 --> 00:06:57.800
If you don't like it,
I'll get you something else.

00:06:58.000 --> 00:06:59.920
I like it very much.

00:06:59.950 --> 00:07:02.160
Apart from Chang'an and Aunt Ning,

00:07:02.270 --> 00:07:04.040
no one has treated me as well as you, Master.

00:07:04.240 --> 00:07:05.750
I never dreamed

00:07:05.750 --> 00:07:08.240
I could live in a house this nice

00:07:08.270 --> 00:07:10.090
or wear clothes this lovely.

00:07:15.240 --> 00:07:16.270
Thank you, Master.

00:07:20.480 --> 00:07:22.190
I'll be here for you.

00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:24.480
Things will only get better.

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:25.720
Mm.

00:07:30.310 --> 00:07:31.830
Commander, His Majesty summons you.

00:07:42.390 --> 00:07:43.270
It's been a long time.

00:07:43.480 --> 00:07:44.720
Wish you well, Auntie

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:45.950
and my younger siblings.

00:07:47.560 --> 00:07:49.160
With the trouble you've stirred,

00:07:49.190 --> 00:07:50.390
how could we be fine?

00:07:51.270 --> 00:07:53.000
Not only did you cause a scene,

00:07:53.070 --> 00:07:56.360
but you also became the first woman
who cast off her husband.

00:07:56.920 --> 00:07:58.190
It's completely

00:07:58.190 --> 00:07:59.720
unprecedented.

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:01.560
How could you...?

00:08:04.680 --> 00:08:06.360
I am the first to do so,

00:08:06.680 --> 00:08:07.750
but I believe

00:08:08.040 --> 00:08:10.240
more women will make the same choice.

00:08:10.950 --> 00:08:12.480
If marriage isn't working out,

00:08:12.480 --> 00:08:13.630
they should have the courage

00:08:14.000 --> 00:08:16.390
to choose to live as they wish.

00:08:16.630 --> 00:08:18.390
You sound completely ridiculous.

00:08:18.680 --> 00:08:21.270
What you have done is utterly rebellious,

00:08:21.480 --> 00:08:23.720
yet you want more people to follow suit.

00:08:24.360 --> 00:08:26.390
For a woman, ignorance is virtue.

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:29.480
Your studies have made you foolish.

00:08:32.550 --> 00:08:33.550
Get up.

00:08:36.790 --> 00:08:38.550
I have a question for you, Auntie.

00:08:38.960 --> 00:08:41.670
If Wanzhen were to marry a man

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:43.750
who treats her badly,

00:08:43.930 --> 00:08:45.200
preferring his concubine over her

00:08:45.510 --> 00:08:47.750
and trying to kill her,

00:08:48.150 --> 00:08:49.550
what would you suggest she do?

00:08:51.120 --> 00:08:52.550
How dare you curse your sister?

00:08:52.670 --> 00:08:53.670
Let go of my mother.

00:08:54.360 --> 00:08:55.200
Let go.

00:08:58.360 --> 00:08:59.390
If you call it a curse,

00:08:59.550 --> 00:09:00.550
then so be it.

00:09:01.080 --> 00:09:01.920
Chang'an, let's go.

00:09:02.840 --> 00:09:04.320
Your sister remains unbetrothed,

00:09:04.390 --> 00:09:05.720
as does your brother.

00:09:06.070 --> 00:09:08.590
A woman who cast off her husband
returning to her natal family

00:09:08.790 --> 00:09:10.550
is both a laughingstock

00:09:10.550 --> 00:09:11.960
and a shame for the Xu family.

00:09:12.440 --> 00:09:15.870
How can your siblings hold up their heads?

00:09:20.390 --> 00:09:22.910
Are you afraid I'll ruin their prospects?

00:09:23.480 --> 00:09:24.510
Isn't that the truth?

00:09:25.750 --> 00:09:27.960
I'm the legitimate eldest daughter
of the Xu Family.

00:09:28.270 --> 00:09:29.270
Father told me

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:31.030
the Xu family would

00:09:31.030 --> 00:09:33.150
welcome me back anytime.

00:09:33.840 --> 00:09:35.360
If it displeases you,

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:37.000
feel free to tattle to Father.

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:38.120
After all these years,

00:09:38.200 --> 00:09:40.720
I never imagined my sister would
act like a village shrew,

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:42.840
with no sense of propriety or shame.

00:09:43.440 --> 00:09:45.510
Your child is watching.

00:09:45.790 --> 00:09:47.630
Aren't you ashamed as a mother?

00:09:47.630 --> 00:09:49.390
My mother entered

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:51.390
and knelt to greet you all,

00:09:51.790 --> 00:09:54.240
showing her respect.

00:09:54.630 --> 00:09:56.510
But you just kept blaming

00:09:56.510 --> 00:09:58.240
and humiliating her,

00:09:58.380 --> 00:09:59.840
showing neither respect nor courtesy.

00:09:59.910 --> 00:10:02.120
So who truly lacks propriety and shame?

00:10:02.960 --> 00:10:04.360
You impudent brat.

00:10:04.550 --> 00:10:06.440
Sharp-tongued
and disrespectful to your elders.

00:10:06.520 --> 00:10:07.510
Time you learned.

00:10:07.510 --> 00:10:08.440
You fool!

00:10:09.840 --> 00:10:10.680
Dad.

00:10:13.550 --> 00:10:14.720
As an uncle,

00:10:14.980 --> 00:10:16.080
laying hands on your nephew

00:10:16.190 --> 00:10:17.240
is utterly improper.

00:10:17.510 --> 00:10:18.960
He was disrespected to me first.

00:10:19.390 --> 00:10:20.320
I heard everything.

00:10:20.480 --> 00:10:21.390
You are at fault here.

00:10:24.150 --> 00:10:25.000
Daddy.

00:10:25.080 --> 00:10:25.920
My child.

00:10:26.480 --> 00:10:27.320
You've endured a lot.

00:10:28.360 --> 00:10:29.270
If I'd known

00:10:29.600 --> 00:10:31.360
how vile Cui Yunfeng was,

00:10:31.790 --> 00:10:32.720
I would've killed him

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:33.560
to defend your honor.

00:10:35.550 --> 00:10:36.630
Dad, don't worry.

00:10:37.200 --> 00:10:38.630
I've dealt with it all.

00:10:39.270 --> 00:10:40.120
I'm troubled no more.

00:10:40.120 --> 00:10:41.440
You may not be troubled,

00:10:41.720 --> 00:10:43.630
but the Xu family will be in big trouble now.

00:10:43.880 --> 00:10:44.840
Stop complaining.

00:10:45.240 --> 00:10:46.080
Master,

00:10:46.440 --> 00:10:47.390
I don't mind

00:10:47.390 --> 00:10:48.600
Wanning's staying.

00:10:48.750 --> 00:10:51.270
But you can't ignore Wanzhen and Qingyuan.

00:10:51.550 --> 00:10:52.910
Wanning's reputation is ruined.

00:10:53.390 --> 00:10:56.270
What if it affects their marriage prospects?

00:10:56.360 --> 00:10:57.200
Nonsense!

00:10:58.910 --> 00:11:00.270
My daughter suffered injustice.

00:11:00.440 --> 00:11:03.000
The Xu family will naturally shield her.

00:11:03.630 --> 00:11:06.790
In the future,
if Wanzhen and Qingyuan suffers,

00:11:07.240 --> 00:11:09.270
we'll receive them just the same.

00:11:09.910 --> 00:11:10.910
Moreover,

00:11:11.240 --> 00:11:12.440
I proclaim seriously

00:11:12.630 --> 00:11:13.470
that from now on,

00:11:13.720 --> 00:11:14.720
whoever makes Wanning

00:11:14.840 --> 00:11:16.390
and Chang'an suffer even the slightest

00:11:16.640 --> 00:11:17.840
will face my wrath.

00:11:18.470 --> 00:11:19.670
I'll protect them with my all.

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:29.320
Master Xu,

00:11:29.670 --> 00:11:31.080
the authorities found

00:11:31.320 --> 00:11:32.550
prohibited Hongzhen Incense

00:11:32.550 --> 00:11:34.120
aboard your merchant vessels.

00:11:34.480 --> 00:11:36.150
You're suspected of illegal trading.

00:11:36.150 --> 00:11:37.870
We need you to come with us.

00:11:40.320 --> 00:11:41.160
Officers.

00:11:41.750 --> 00:11:42.910
It must be a misunderstanding.

00:11:43.120 --> 00:11:45.320
Since I started doing business

00:11:45.320 --> 00:11:47.320
I've always followed the law in my business

00:11:47.320 --> 00:11:48.870
and never dealt with prohibited goods.

00:11:49.440 --> 00:11:50.890
How could there be Hongzhen Incense?

00:11:51.050 --> 00:11:51.960
That's right, Lord Pei.

00:11:52.200 --> 00:11:53.240
Could there be a mistake?

00:11:54.460 --> 00:11:56.030
The Jinlin Guards uphold justice fairly.

00:11:56.360 --> 00:11:59.000
We don't arrest without solid evidence.

00:12:03.030 --> 00:12:03.870
Wait.

00:12:04.150 --> 00:12:04.990
Lord Pei,

00:12:05.120 --> 00:12:06.790
my father's integrity is well known.

00:12:06.960 --> 00:12:08.360
He would never do such a thing.

00:12:09.870 --> 00:12:10.720
Don't worry.

00:12:11.200 --> 00:12:12.720
If your father is innocent,

00:12:13.150 --> 00:12:14.390
I'll definitely clear his name.

00:12:15.630 --> 00:12:16.960
Things are complicated right now,

00:12:17.630 --> 00:12:18.630
and I need some time.

00:12:21.960 --> 00:12:22.800
Daddy,

00:12:24.070 --> 00:12:25.470
go with them and try not to worry.

00:12:26.000 --> 00:12:27.480
Our conscience is clear.

00:12:27.480 --> 00:12:28.960
I believe the Jinlin Guards

00:12:29.360 --> 00:12:30.750
will prove your innocence.

00:12:31.120 --> 00:12:31.960
Mm.

00:12:32.720 --> 00:12:33.560
Take him.

00:12:35.870 --> 00:12:36.750
Mother.

00:12:37.510 --> 00:12:38.510
Mother.

00:12:47.320 --> 00:12:48.670
Lady Xu, actually,

00:12:48.910 --> 00:12:50.030
Commander Pei worked hard

00:12:50.030 --> 00:12:51.480
to protect your father.

00:12:52.080 --> 00:12:54.720
Your father was facing immediate conviction,

00:12:55.120 --> 00:12:57.480
but Commander staked his own future
to vouch for him.

00:12:57.600 --> 00:12:59.210
He made a military pledge to His Majesty,

00:12:59.670 --> 00:13:01.550
thus securing a month to investigate.

00:13:02.100 --> 00:13:04.600
If he can't find crucial evidence
within a month,

00:13:05.270 --> 00:13:07.360
not only will your father face grave danger,

00:13:07.360 --> 00:13:09.440
but the Commander will be implicated too.

00:13:21.240 --> 00:13:22.270
Xu Wanning,

00:13:22.520 --> 00:13:24.240
you think
killing me will be the end of it?

00:13:24.510 --> 00:13:25.550
You will pay for this!

00:13:26.270 --> 00:13:27.870
Someone will come after you for me.

00:13:29.840 --> 00:13:31.600
(I disrupted the Hongzhen Incense trade,)

00:13:31.670 --> 00:13:34.630
(so the person behind it
wants to hurt my father.)

00:13:59.420 --> 00:14:02.540
♪The old house's door remains
tightly shut♪

00:14:02.740 --> 00:14:06.620
♪Snow covers the stone table in front♪

00:14:07.340 --> 00:14:10.460
♪The you and I who once laughed♪

00:14:10.460 --> 00:14:13.620
♪Now only I am left alone♪

00:14:13.620 --> 00:14:17.020
♪Snowflakes fall, blurring my sight♪

00:14:17.220 --> 00:14:20.660
♪As if trying to hide this farewell♪

00:14:21.060 --> 00:14:24.460
♪Yet the pain feels so real♪

00:14:24.620 --> 00:14:27.780
♪Growing sharper in the snow♪

00:14:27.940 --> 00:14:31.460
♪Snow falls across the city,
filling my heart♪

00:14:31.460 --> 00:14:35.420
♪The cold wind blows
through a lonely corner♪

00:14:35.780 --> 00:14:38.900
♪Jade fragments drift
in the wandering snow♪

00:14:38.900 --> 00:14:41.900
♪My heart sinks
into the vast frozen river♪

00:14:42.180 --> 00:14:45.940
♪Time wears on
as snow falls again and again♪

00:14:45.940 --> 00:14:49.300
♪Just like your endless heartlessness♪

00:14:49.540 --> 00:14:52.900
♪Frosted branches shake off stardust♪

00:14:53.100 --> 00:14:56.180
♪It's my endless devotion to you♪

00:14:56.460 --> 00:14:59.820
♪Snow falls across the city,
filling my heart♪

00:15:00.060 --> 00:15:03.300
♪That pure white is an endless longing♪

00:15:03.590 --> 00:15:06.940
♪The wind can't scatter the snow
it piles into a cocoon♪

00:15:07.140 --> 00:15:10.460
♪Trapping me in this winter♪

00:15:10.660 --> 00:15:14.020
♪Snow fills the city,
drifting toward the horizon♪

00:15:14.260 --> 00:15:17.820
♪Carrying away the sorrow of farewells♪

00:15:18.060 --> 00:15:21.660
♪I linger alone in the snow♪

00:15:21.660 --> 00:15:25.900
♪Waiting for a fate
that will never come♪